                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34t6fp5j/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">As promised I send<lb/> you the sermon I delivered<lb/> in\n                    <add>שבועות</add> last, I have written<lb/> it close and on both sides to<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">save postage</hi> to which I know<lb/> you will not object. I\n                hope it will<lb/> suit your columns—and if so<lb/> I shall always be pleased to\n                send<lb/> you some, not minding the trouble<lb/> of transcribing, as you know\n                such<lb/> occupies time—notice the <hi rend=\"underline\">Gleaner</hi><lb/> of the\n                        <date>13<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> June</date> about <add>גרורית</add><lb/> and\n                you will see the able excuse<lb/> of the Editor—more anon.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">H. A. Henry</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <date>June 18<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1862</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>P.S.</p>\n            <p>I leave you to put<lb/> the heading to the sermon—</p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_20_6.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 20 No. 6 pages 251 through 259. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34t6fp5j/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
